g.title: Name : Resize_98 Info : INFORMATION -- [TIDL_ResizeLayer] Any resize ratio which is power of 2 and greater than 4 will be placed by combination of 4x4 resize layer and 2x2 resize layer. For example a 8x8 resize will be replaced by 4x4 resize followed by 2x2 resize.
